subject: Baseball
Doping (Sports)
Suits and Litigation (Civil)
lead_paragraph: Major League Baseball is seeking the dismissal of a suit by Yankees third baseman Alex Rodriguez that challenges a season-long suspension for the use of prohibited performance-enhancing substances.
